src_text: Swiluva swa Mpfukelo (Xitereko) , hi tsundzuka ntirho wa vavasati tanihi vatumbuluxi va nhlangano wa vavasati etikweni leri, hi ku tekela enhlokweni leswaku loko u nyika matimba eka wansati, u nyika matimba eka rixakTanihi tiko hi humelerile eka swo tala endzhawini ya ku nyikiwa ka matimba eka vavasat Ku nga si fika 1994 Palamende a yi ri na vuyimeri bya 2,7% bya vavasati, naswona ku landzela mihlawulo yo sungula ya xidemokirasi, vuyimeri bya vavasati eka Huvo ya Rixaka byi vi le eka 27,7%.
trg_text: statement, we commemorate the role of women as pioneers of the women's movement in this country, recognising that when you empower a woman, you empower the natioAs a country we have achieved a lot in the field of women empowermen Prior to 1994 Parliament had a mere 2,7% representation of women, and following the first democratic elections, women representation in the National Assembly stood at 27,7%.

src_text: Eduardo dos Santos wa Angola, loyi a chikaka exitulwini endzhaku ka 37 wa malembe a ri Phuresidente no rhangela eku humeseni ka tiko ra yena eka nyimpi ya xin wana manana yo leh Xandla xa Phuresidente Ramaphosa, eka xiyimo xa yena xa Muleteri wa SADC eka Mfumo wa Lesotho, u ta tlhela a andlala xiviko eka Samiti ya SADC Double Troika leyi nga ta khomeriwa ePitori hi ti 18 Mhawuri, laha Mfumo wa Lesotho wu languteriweke ku andlala kungu ra mipfuxet Leswi swi landzela mimbhurisano exikarhi ka Xandla xa Phuresidente na mfumo lowuntshwa, varhangeri va mavandla yo kokela etlhelo, kholeji ya tihosi na swirho swa vaakatiko eka Mfumo, ku tshetsha ndlela ya ntirhiso wo helela wa swiboho swa SADC eka mipfuxeto ya sekithara ya milawu na vuhlayisek Khabinete yi amukela mimbuyelo yo suka eka Phuresidente Jacob Zuma loko a rhurherile Phuresidente Ellen Johnson Sirleaf wa Rhiphabuliki ra Liberia, enkarhini wa Rendzo ra Mfum Matiko hamambirhi ya pfumerile ku languta eka ku antswisa mbango lowu pfumelelaka ku olovisa maendlelo yo endla bindzu ematikweni ya hin Khabinete yi hlohlotela tikhamphani ta mabindzu lawa ya nga ri ki ya mfumo ku vekisa eLiberiMavandla ya pfumerile ku hetisisa ku sayiniwa ka Ntwanano wa Nsuso wa Visa eka Vakhomi va Tiphasipoto ta Xidipulomati na ta Ximfum Va tlhele va pfumela ku hatlisisa mimbhurisano na ku hetisisa switirho swin wana swa matlhelo hamambirhi eka vurimi, vupfhumba, rihanyo, eneji, mati na nkululo exikarhi ka swin wan Khabinete yi hoyozela vanhu va Rwanda ku va vi le na nhlawulo lowu nga na ku rhula lowu voneke ku hlawuriwa nakambe ka Phuresidente Paul Kagam Ku hetisisiwa ka ku hlawula kun wana loku humeleleke eAfrika i xikombiso xa ku hluvukisiwa ka xidemokirasi loku ya ka emahlweni etikweninkul.

src_text: Khabinete yi tlhele yi hlangana na AU eku hoyozeleni ka Kenya eku fambiseni ka mihlawulo leyi humelelek Sweswi swa boha leswaku vaakatiko hinkwavo va Kenya va amukela mimbuyelo ya mihlawulo no tirhela ntwanano wa rixaka etikwenBRIC Phuresidente Zuma namuntlha, 17 Mhawuri 2017, u ta fambisa ku simekiwa ximfumo ka Senthara ya Xifundza ya Afrika ya le Brazil, Russia, India, China na Afrika-Dzonga (BRICS) Bangi Yintshwa ya Nhluvukiso (NDB) eHotela Michelangelo, eSandto Ku simekiwa ka Senthara ya Xifundzha ya Afrika yi ta kombisa ku nyikiwa ka vukorhokeri bya NDB, ku kombisa vuswikoti bya ntirho wa bangi eka xivandla xa switirhisiwa na nhluvukiso wa nkarhi wo leha eka matiko lawa ya humelelaka no hluvuk.

trg_text: Upcoming events Cabinet reiterates President Zuma s call, reminding members of the public to nominate persons from all walks of life deserving to receive the country s highest honours, the National Orders, in April next yeaThe ceremony honours South Africans and eminent foreign nationals who have excelled in various fieldNominations forms are available on The Presidency s website (wwthepresidencgoza), Thusong Service Centres, municipal offices and constituency office A short motivation of the person nominated should be attache The 2018 National Orders nominations will close on 31 August 2012.

src_text: Ku nghenelela swi ta seketela Vutshamaxitulu bya Afrika-Dzonga bya Nhlangano wa Rim wa Lwandle ra India hi 2017/18.Afrika-Dzonga ri ta tirhisa xibye xa rona xa ndzavisiso SA Agulhas II ku endla ndzavisiso wa le lwandle loko ri ri karhi ri letela no aka tshaku ra swa sayense eka Afrika-Dzonga na Afrika VuhumadyambKu hlengeletiwa ka switiviwa swa le mbangwini swa masungulo swa nkarhi wo leha swi ta veka matiko lawa ya ha hluvukaka ya Rim ya Lwandle ra le India eka xiyimo xo antswa ku hlayisa xindzhuti xa lwandle ra rona ku kuma tindlela to khiyinula vuswikoti bya wona bya tiikhonomi ta le lwandle ku antswisa vutomi bya vaakatiko va won Khabinete yi hlamuseriwile hi tshalatshala ra Ikhonomi ya Tikhemikhali na Malakatsa ya Tilebe ta Phakisa, leri vekiweke leswaku ri sungula hi Mhawuri 2017.

src_text: Khabinete yi hlamuseriwile hi swikombelo swo hlaya ku kumisisa mindzelekano ya swindzankulu emigangeni eka swifundzankulu swo hambanahamban Exikarhi ka tindzhawu leti khumbhekeke ku na Masipala wa Muganga wa Elias Motsoaledi, Masipala wa Muganga wa Marblehall na Masipala wa Muganga wa MatatielMiganga leyi yi vurile swivangelo swo hlaya swa swikombelo leswi, swo fana na ndzhawu laha yi kumekaka kona na mfikelelo wa vukorhoker Swikombelo swi amukeriwile hi Bodo ya Mindzelekano ya Masipala na Ndzawulo ya Mfumontirhisano na Timhaka ta XintMindzelekano ya swifundzankulu yi vuriwile eka Vumbiw Ku anakanyiwa kun wana na kun wana ka swikombelo leswi sweswo ku fanele ku endliwa endzeni ka rimba ra vumbiwKhabinete yi pfumerile leswaku phurosese yo kumisisa nakambe mindzelekano, yi ta katsa leswaku Matatiele, ku sunguriwa hi yon Phurosese leyi ya palamende yi ta tlhela yi katsa nghenelelo wa vanhu tanihileswi swi lavekisaka xiswona hi Vumbiwa na nawu Mitlangu leyi ta ka Khabinete yi tiyisisa xikombelo xa Phuresidente Zuma, xo tsundzuxa swirho swa vanhu ku hlawula vanhu ku suka eka swiyimo hinkwaswo lava faneleke ku kuma mixiximo ya le henhla ya tiko, Swileriso swa Rixaka, hi Dzivamisoko lembe leri ta kNtirho wu xixima MaAfrika-Dzonga na vaaki va le matikwenimambe vo hlawuleka lava tirheke hi matimba eka swivandla swo hambanahambanTifomo to hlawula ta kumeka eka webusayiti ya Hofisi ya Phuresidente (wwthepresidencgoza), Thusong Service Centres, tihofisi ta ka masipala na tihofisis ta vaak Nhlohlotelo wo koma wa munhu loyi a hlawuriwaka wu fanele ku khomanisiw Mihlawulo ya Swileriso swa Rixaka ya 2018 yi ta pfala hi ti 31 Mhawuri 2012.
